  "text": "Most of the previous methods only model the entities and relations, and ignore the abundant entity attributes. Our method can easily model a large number of entity attribute triples. In order to prove the efficiency, we extract the attribute triples from the FB24k [CITATION_1] dataset to build the evaluation dataset called FB15k-237-Attr.",
